  "title": "Service Engineer (Refrigeration System/Analyzer/No Experience Required) LT85",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform diagnose, preventive and maintenance, trouble-shooting and repair of refrigeration system.</p></li><li><p>Installation and commissioning of new refrigeration system. Ensure proper set-up and functionality as well as conducting user training.</p></li><li><p>Maintain service maintenance checklists, documentation and upkeep of service tools and test equipment.</p></li><li><p>Ad hoc tasks as assigned.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum NITEC in Engineering (Mechanical/Electronics/Electrical), or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of refrigeration gas, electronic, mechanical, refrigeration and heating system.</p></li><li><p>Technical knowledge and hands-on skills on monitoring, troubleshooting, servicing and maintenance.</p></li><li><p>Able to do troubleshooting and interpret technical drawings (e.g. P&ID, wiring diagram, loop diagram, schematic diagram, connection details, hook-up drawing).</p></li><li><p>Knowledge and experience in welding & brazing will be an added advantage.</p></li><li><p>Proactive with good initiatives, problem solving skill and analytical ability.</p></li></ul><p>HOW TO APPLY:</p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format to leo.tang(at)trustrecruit.com.sg</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tang For Farn (Leo)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24121981</p>",
